org.eclipse.viatra.dse.visualizer

Class GraphmlDesignSpaceVisualizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.visualizer.GraphmlDesignSpaceVisualizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDesignSpaceVisualizer, IExploreEventHandler

    public class GraphmlDesignSpaceVisualizer
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDesignSpaceVisualizer
    This class implements the IDesignSpaceVisualizer interface by storing the trace of the exploration into its own data structure and exporting it to .graphml. It only supports single threaded exploration.
